    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puppet Seed is a Sandbox CRPG created by a Solo Developer using Unreal Engine 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The minimum requirement for GPU Vram is 6gb. Demo available below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puppet Seed combines two game features which are rarely seen together. Permanent, customizable AI Companions and a seamless, non level-gated, 3D Open World. Collect, train and upgrade unique party members with modular armor, weapons and skills as well as summoning powerful combat monsters. Explore the frozen surface of Echora on foot as well as using your player owned vehicle, defeating opponents in a non-linear, sandbox world. Be mindful that your reputation matters, the conflicts you chose will determine which groups will hunt you and which ones will open new trade opportunities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348980/extras/b7483309fafc89be0515bf520628f03a.avif?t=1732900208\" width=620 height=310 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348980/extras/6efcb31d943c80b7fae21cb4c736ee89.poster.avif?t=1732900208\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348980/extras/6efcb31d943c80b7fae21cb4c736ee89.webm?t=1732900208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348980/extras/6efcb31d943c80b7fae21cb4c736ee89.mp4?t=1732900208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348980/extras/7dbd71512049b62267357c526d41f0e0.avif?t=1732900208\" width=624 height=351 /></span><span